4dda0dc","tid":1656902,"uid":44377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:37:26.000Z","msg":"budapest個夜景我覺得好靚喎，我好鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13190a5940f126bae301cb5cb9126d5ef1b4325b","tid":1656902,"uid":61546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:46:18.000Z","msg":"唔係深度遊嘅4日ok<br />\n錢可以帶少量EURO，落地可以兌做HUF福林用嚟搭車。唔帶亦都唔係問題，因為依家Budapest主要車站都有自動售票機畀你用信用卡買車飛。另外市內大部分OTP Bank嘅ATM都可以經銀聯ATM卡直接拎錢，好方便。"},{"pid":"20480e62d3d55dd8141ece6b9a8db1b8cc066895","tid":1656902,"uid":61546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bee81fb009543baba1612fda40ac589aeb78967","tid":1656902,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:21:06.000Z","msg":"三日夠<br />\n夜晚爬山望夜景呢就伏嘅，又凍個景又唔靚，因為好多建築都唔會開燈<br />\n我上次浸温泉浸完身上好多紅點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:57:27.000Z","msg":"夜景嚟講Budapest係Danube沿河嚟講最靚嘅city<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講開上山睇夜景，最出名一定係Citadella。布達城堡Buda Castle、鏈橋 Chain Bridge、瑪格麗特橋Margit Bridge同伊利沙伯橋Elisabeth Bridge，仲有Danube河景一眼望晒。<br />\n如果唔想行上山，可以搭地鐵M4綠色線去M&oacute;ricz Zsigmond k&ouml;rt&eacute;r M 搭27號巴士。"},{"pid":"a8d07fb18704cd2c300a5c193509bdd56236f2e3","tid":1656902,"uid":297346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:47:09.000Z","msg":"可以去 Gelarto Rosa 食gelato<br />\n<br />\nKiskakukk Restaurant 呢間既鵝肝牛排 /鵝肝蘋果都唔錯，如果comme chez soi冇開可以去呢間"},{"pid":"f1bdde5d323caa03757c0044727678078aeea6a5","tid":1656902,"uid":326463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:42:19.000Z","msg":"上網睇好似有兩個浴場邊個先啱"},{"pid":"0f6aff7f4fa7d772ec960dec4c7d97e800bd90e1","tid":1656902,"uid":61546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1bdde5d323caa03757c0044727678078aeea6a5","tid":1656902,"uid":326463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:42:19.000Z","msg":"上網睇好似有兩個浴場邊個先啱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:20:18.0